trait_name: leaf area per leaf dry mass
method: SLA was solely obtained via field measurements and calculated on three leaves (from separate individuals) by scanning leaves and analysing the images with Image J (Abramoff, Magalhaes & Ram 2004), petioles were excluded from the analysis. Leaf area for grasses was acquired using the leaf blade (i.e. the portion of the leaf above the sheath and ligule).
